        "body": "<p>Topic has been opened but not answered for a different device Huawei P8 <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33669464/android-logcat-error-zipfilecache-init-failed-when-open-zip-file-device-spec\">here<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>I`m using Huawei G8 with Andoid 5.1 and get the same error plus another one in Android Studio:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>1) E/HAL﹕ hw_get_module_by_class: lib loaded: /system/lib64/hw/gralloc.msm8916.so\n2) E/ZipFileCache﹕ init failed when open zip file.\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>As i cant comment yet reputation-wise I would like to ask again: <\/p>\n\n<p><strong>- what can cause above errors?<br>\n- any workaround possible, or is it a vendor-/device specific problem (Huawei)?<br>\n- will this effect the final app on release?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<p>In dev the app is sometimes running slow or seems to sleep due to the errors. They dont appear in the Nexus emulator.<\/p>\n",
